task.summary: Added test classes for more clear idea of how hiarchy in Intellij works vs Netbeans for George+Neethan
Added example on how to use DataPull api as a library. This example gets the temperature of two cities, compares them, and outputs a description.
The beginnings of the Observer pattern. Interfaces for the subject and observers, as well as class to store observers in an array list.
